Package: GSOD
Type: Package
Title: Download, Clean and Generate New Variables From GSOD Weather Data
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-03-22
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Adam Sparks <ahsparks@gmail.com> [aut, cre]",
    "Tomislav Hengl <tom.hengl@wur.nl> [ctb]",
    "Andy Nelson <dr.andy.nelson@gmail.com [ctb]",
    "Kay Sumfleth <kay@sumfleth.de> [ctb]"
  ))
Maintainer: Adam H Sparks, <adamhsparks@gmail.com>
Description: Automatic downloading and cleaning data from the Global Summary of
    the Day (GSOD) data provided by the US National Climatic Data Center (NCDC).
    Stations are individually checked for number of missing days to assure data
    quality, stations with too many missing observations are omitted. Output is
    .csv file summarizing each year, which includes vapor pressure and
    relative humidity variables calcuated from GSOD data.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
License: GPL (>= 3)
Imports: dplyr, lubridate
